headline: Home Sales Fell 4.9% in January, Extending Slump in Housing Market
summary: Home prices and mortgage rates, which were a drag on home sales for most of 2024, stayed elevated and put off many buyers.

headline: CoStar Targets Australia’s Domain With $1.68 Billion Takeover Proposal
summary: U.S. real-estate advertiser and analytics provider CoStar is looking to follow its recent U.K. expansion with a move into Australia.
